title: Marked Men (1940 Western) Six Fugitives Break For Freedom! with Isabel Jewell

sources.title: Marked Men (1940 Western) Six Fugitives Break For Freedom! with Isabel Jewell
sources.description:
Marked Men (also known as Desert Escape ) is a 1940 American film directed by Sam Newfield, using the pseudonym "Sherman Scott"

Plot Summary:

Wrongfully accused and on the run, Bill Carver braves the desert with his dog, Wolf, to outmaneuver ruthless criminals, survive relentless dangers, and fight to clear his name.


Main Actors:
Warren Hull - Bill Carver
Isabel Jewell - Linda Harkness
John Dilson - Dr James Prentiss Harkness
Paul Bryar - Joe Mallon
Charles Williams - Charlie Sloane
Lyle Clement - Marshal Dan Tait
Budd Buster - Mr Marvin (the Druggist)
Al St. John - Gimpy (a Thug)
Eddie Fetherston - Marty (a Thug)
Ted Erwin - Mike (a Thug)
Art Miles - Blimp (a Thug)
Grey Shadow - Wolf (the Dog)
